    "url": "admin-user-subscriptions.html",
    "title": "Subscriber Plans",
    "content": "Subscriber Plans  WAPI Documentation Top Purchase Support Frontend Admin A A A Wapi documentation Subscriber Plans Close Introduction Prerequisite Wapi Installation Overview Frontend Installation Backend Installation Local Server Live Server Database Seed Deployment Cpanel Virtual Private Server Vercel Core Features Advanced Features Usage Admin Usage Tenant Usage Agent Usage Admin Guide Dashboard Payment Transactions Users Short Links Subscription Manage Plans Subscriber Plans Manage Users All Users Add User Content Management Manage FAQs Manage Testimonials Pages Roles  Permissions Manage Landing Templates Library System Settings Payment Gateways Settings AI Models Languages Currencies Taxes Contact Inquiries Frontend Guide Dashboard WA Chat Chat Appearance Integrations Integrate WABA WABA Phone Numbers Templates Tools Tags Media Teams Agents Automations Automation Builder Predefined Actions Response Resources Keyword Trigger AI Call Assistant WhatsApp Form My Subscription Subscriptions Marketing Campaigns Orders Catalogues Webhooks Contacts Columns Import Jobs AI Config Developer Menu Subscriber Plans Subscription Lifecycle  Insights The Subscriber Plans module centralizes customer relationship and recurring revenue management It provides a realtime view of plan commitments billing status and service states across the platform View and manage customer subscriptions payment status and plan assignments 1 Manual Subscription Approval When a user initiates a Manual Subscription eg via Offline Payment the system places the request in a pending state Administrators retain full authority to review these transactions Accept Request Approving the request immediately activates the subscribers chosen plan and starts the billing cycle Reject Request Rejecting the request prevents plan activation Users are typically notified to provide valid payment proof 2 Data Architecture  Management Identity Customer name and email verification Plan Tier Assigned subscription and billing frequency Financials Paid amount and gateway details Timeline Term validity with startend timestamps Auditing View granular logs  invoices Migration Adjust tiers or billing frequency Governance Stop renewals or extend access Key Benefits Billing Control Rapid response to payment issues Churn Risk Proactive tracking of expiring terms Data Hygiene Realtime synchronization with gateways Troubleshooting Missing Entry Refresh data or clear active filters Status Mismatch Verify gateway webhook connectivity Failed Payment Check primary payment method validity Copyright 2026  WAPI  WhatsApp Marketing Platform by PixelStrap"
