    "url": "admin-users-short-links.html",
    "title": "Users Short Links",
    "content": "Users Short Links  WAPI Documentation Top Purchase Support Frontend Admin A A A Wapi documentation Users Short Links Close Introduction Prerequisite Wapi Installation Overview Frontend Installation Backend Installation Local Server Live Server Database Seed Deployment Cpanel Virtual Private Server Vercel Core Features Advanced Features Usage Admin Usage Tenant Usage Agent Usage Admin Guide Dashboard Payment Transactions Users Short Links Subscription Manage Plans Subscriber Plans Manage Users All Users Add User Content Management Manage FAQs Manage Testimonials Pages Roles  Permissions Manage Landing Templates Library System Settings Payment Gateways Settings AI Models Languages Currencies Taxes Contact Inquiries Frontend Guide Dashboard WA Chat Chat Appearance Integrations Integrate WABA WABA Phone Numbers Templates Tools Tags Media Teams Agents Automations Automation Builder Predefined Actions Response Resources Keyword Trigger AI Call Assistant WhatsApp Form My Subscription Subscriptions Marketing Campaigns Orders Catalogues Webhooks Contacts Columns Import Jobs AI Config Developer Menu 1 Strategic Overview Master Governance for WhatsApp Short Links The Users Short Links module is a powerful administrative tool that provides a centralized view of all WhatsApp access points created by platform users This feature is essential for monitoring engagement ensuring compliance and understanding how users are driving traffic to their business numbers Link Management View and manage the full catalog of custom WhatsApp links across all user accounts Engagement Tracking Monitor clickthrough rates and link usage to identify highperforming communication strategies Central Control Enable disable or remove links to maintain platform integrity and security 2 Administrative Viewport The primary interface is designed for speed and clarity allowing administrators to audit thousands of access points through an optimized data grid Short Link Catalog A comprehensive list showing usergenerated short URLs Advanced Filtering Quickly isolate links by user ID phone number or creation age Engagement Metrics Realtime click counters visible directly in the management table 3 Link Property Breakdown Each record provides a granular view of the links identity and its owners configuration Identity  Origins Link ID Systemgenerated unique identifier User info Current owner of the short link WhatsApp Number The target destination for the link Status  Performance Clicks Total engagement count since inception Status Current availability ActiveDraftInactive Created Date Timestamp of the initial link generation Central Management Total visibility across your entire user base from a single screen Better Insights Understand which marketing channels are driving the most WhatsApp traffic Link Hygiene Maintain a clean platform by auditing and disabling unused or broken links Copyright 2026  WAPI  WhatsApp Marketing Platform by PixelStrap"
