    "url": "agent-management.html",
    "title": "Agent Management",
    "content": "Agent Management  Wapi documentation Top Purchase Support Frontend Admin A A A Wapi documentation Agents Management Close Introduction Prerequisite Wapi Installation Overview Frontend Installation Backend Installation Local Server Live Server Database Seed Deployment Cpanel Virtual Private Server Vercel Core Features Advanced Features Usage Admin Usage Tenant Usage Agent Usage Admin Guide Dashboard Payment Transactions Users Short Links Subscription Manage Plans Subscriber Plans Manage Users All Users Add User Content Management Manage FAQs Manage Testimonials Pages Roles  Permissions Manage Landing Templates Library System Settings Payment Gateways Settings AI Models Languages Currencies Taxes Contact Inquiries Frontend Guide Dashboard WA Chat Chat Appearance Integrations Integrate WABA WABA Phone Numbers Templates Tools Tags Media Teams Agents Automations Automation Builder Predefined Actions Response Resources Keyword Trigger AI Call Assistant WhatsApp Form My Subscription Subscriptions Marketing Campaigns Orders Catalogues Webhooks Contacts Columns Import Jobs AI Config Developer Menu Agent Management Scaling Your Support Ecosystem Agents are the frontline of your WhatsApp engagement The Agent Management system allows you to onboard team members link them to strategic teams and monitor their interaction density in realtime Profile Control Manage individual agent identities and visibility settings Team Linking Inherit granular permissions instantly via team assignment Privacy Logic Secure customer data with Hide Phone and module restrictions Agent Intelligence Dashboard Pro Tip For a detailed guide on managing and tracking agent workflows visit the Agent Task Management documentation The primary list view provides a comprehensive audit trail for every team member Monitor status assignments and historical activity from a single interface Identity Name Email and Phone Number Assignment Currently linked strategic Team Lifecycle Creation Date and Active Status Actions Edit Delete and Visibility toggles Agent Onboarding Workflow Follow this standardized protocol to expand your operational capacity Initiate Navigate to Agents and click the  Create Agent button Profile Definition Enter the agents professional name corporate email and WhatsAppenabled phone number Team Integration Select a preconfigured Team from the dropdown This defines their platform permissions Security Settings Toggle the Hide Phone option if you wish to restrict agent access to raw customer numbers Activation Set the status to Active and add any operational notes before saving Critical Association Each agent MUST be linked to a team The team acts as the permission gateway for the agent Lifecycle Management  Governance Fluid Reassignment Easily move agents between Sales and Support teams as your volume fluctuations dictate Instant Offboarding Toggling an agent to Inactive instantly revokes all platform access without deleting logs Visibility Toggles Use the Hide Phone option for contractors or external agents to ensure GDPR compliance Governance Checklist Unique Emails Ensure each agent has a unique corporate email for platform identification Role Alignment Doublecheck team permissions before assigning a new agent Active Status Agents must be Active to appear in the Chat Inbox assignable list Troubleshooting Guide Agent Cannot Login Verify their status is Active and the email matches their profile perfectly Permissions Not Reflecting Try clicking Update Agent again to forcesync the team blueprint permissions Copyright 2026  WAPI  WhatsApp Marketing Platform by PixelStrap"
