    "url": "ai-config.html",
    "title": "AI Configuration",
    "content": "AI Configuration  Wapi Documentation Top Purchase Support Frontend Admin A A A WAPI Documentation Intelligence Core AI Configuration Close Introduction Prerequisite Wapi Installation Overview Frontend Installation Backend Installation Local Server Live Server Database Seed Deployment Cpanel Virtual Private Server Vercel Core Features Advanced Features Usage Admin Usage Tenant Usage Agent Usage Admin Guide Dashboard Payment Transactions Users Short Links Subscription Manage Plans Subscriber Plans Manage Users All Users Add User Content Management Manage FAQs Manage Testimonials Pages Roles  Permissions Manage Landing Templates Library System Settings Payment Gateways Settings AI Models Languages Currencies Taxes Contact Inquiries Frontend Guide Dashboard WA Chat Chat Appearance Integrations Integrate WABA WABA Phone Numbers Templates Tools Tags Media Teams Agents Automations Automation Builder Predefined Actions Response Resources Keyword Trigger AI Call Assistant WhatsApp Form My Subscription Subscriptions Marketing Campaigns Orders Catalogues Webhooks Contacts Columns Import Jobs AI Config Developer Menu AI Configuration 1 Overview The AI Configuration engine integrates LLMs OpenAI Gemini Grok to power smart automated responses and lead qualification with full cost and personality control MultiModel GPT4o Gemini 15 Grok etc Secure Vault Encrypted API key storage Live Status Realtime connectivity pings Strategic Value 247 Support Humanlike automated replies Smart Leads AIdriven categorization Agility Switch models in seconds 2 Dashboard Overview Google Gemini 15 Pro Connected Selector Choose your AI brain Key Vault Secure credential management Monitor Live connectivity validation 3 AI Provider Selection DeepSeek Chat Highvolume efficiency Gemini 15 Pro Multimodal powerhouse GPT4o Creative standard 4 Configuration Protocol Paste your API key into the secure vault Transmission is SHA256 encrypted for maximum security 5 Implementation Lifecycle Select Model  Paste API Key  Ping Validation  AI Activation API Key Acquisition Flow Account Setup Sign up on the providers platform eg OpenAI or Google AI Studio  BillingCredits Ensure you have active credits or a payment method linked Gemini often provides a free tier for developers Create Secret Key Navigate to the API Keys section and click Create New Secret Key  Paste  Secure Copy the key immediately it wont be shown again and paste it into the Wapi AI Config vault Primary Use Cases Smart FAQs Intentbased autoreplies Lead Scoring Qualifying via chat Copy Gen Smart campaign writing Best Practices Match model complexity to task Monitor Connected status daily Rotate API keys every 90 days 6 Troubleshooting Matrix Symptom Cause Fix No Connection Invalid Key Verify on provider panel Model Error Tier Limit Upgrade plan or switch model High Latency Server Load Switch to Lite model  2026 Wapi All rights reserved Premium AI Core Documentation"
