    "url": "catalogues.html",
    "title": "Catalogue Management",
    "content": "Catalogue Management  Wapi documentation Top Purchase Support Frontend Admin A A A Wapi documentation Catalogue Management Close Introduction Prerequisite Wapi Installation Overview Frontend Installation Backend Installation Local Server Live Server Database Seed Deployment Cpanel Virtual Private Server Vercel Core Features Advanced Features Usage Admin Usage Tenant Usage Agent Usage Admin Guide Dashboard Payment Transactions Users Short Links Subscription Manage Plans Subscriber Plans Manage Users All Users Add User Content Management Manage FAQs Manage Testimonials Pages Roles  Permissions Manage Landing Templates Library System Settings Payment Gateways Settings AI Models Languages Currencies Taxes Contact Inquiries Frontend Guide Dashboard WA Chat Chat Appearance Integrations Integrate WABA WABA Phone Numbers Templates Tools Tags Media Teams Agents Automations Automation Builder Predefined Actions Response Resources Keyword Trigger AI Call Assistant WhatsApp Form My Subscription Subscriptions Marketing Campaigns Orders Catalogues Webhooks Contacts Columns Import Jobs AI Config Developer Menu Catalogue Management 1 Overview Catalogue Management enables businesses to synchronize their Meta Facebook Business catalogs with the Wapi platform This seamless integration allows you to showcase manage and sell products directly within WhatsApp conversations and automated commerce workflows Meta Sync Seamless synchronization with Meta Commerce Manager assets Centralized Control Manage all product listings from a single unified dashboard Conversational Commerce Enable customers to browse and purchase products in realtime Automated Sales Support automated selling workflows via AI and campaigns 2 Key Capabilities Leverage the power of integrated commerce with these core functionalities Sync Meta Catalog Connect and import your existing Meta Business Manager catalogs Linked Catalog Overview View and manage all linked catalogs and their statuses Product Management Search filter and organize synced product data WhatsApp Shareable Use products directly in chats campaigns and chatbots Commerce Workflow Enable automated cart submissions and order creation Realtime Updates Regular sync ensures your platform data matches Meta listings 3 Meta Catalogue Integration Follow these steps to connect your Facebook Business catalog with the platform Step 1 Connect Meta Account Navigate to Catalogue settings and authorize your Meta Facebook Business account via OAuth Step 2 Select Catalogue Choose the specific catalog from your Meta Commerce Manager that you wish to synchronize Step 3 Protocol Synchronization Initiate the initial sync The platform will import all product titles IDs pricing and media assets Step 4 Link to WABA Verify the link between your synced catalog and your active WhatsApp Business Account WABA for direct commerce messaging Requirement Only approved and active catalogs from Meta Commerce Manager can be synced Ensure proper admin permissions in Meta Business Manager 4 Operational Management Manage Products Once synced access the Manage Products dashboard to review imported listings View Listings Review sync status images and pricing Search  Filter Quickly locate specific SKUs or categories Listing Organization Group products for various sales workflows Syncing Protocol Product data is imported securely into the system for automation use Synced Attributes Product Names MediaImages Live Pricing Descriptions Availability 5 Strategic Operational Governance Deployment  Best Practices MultiChannel Usage Share products in Live Chat AIpowered bots and Broadcast campaigns Source Integrity Maintain your catalog in Meta Commerce Manager Wapi ensures data synchronization Conversion Focus Use highresolution media and accurate pricing to drive customer trust and sales Protocol Troubleshooting Missing Inventory Verify that your catalogue is correctly linked to your WABA in Meta Permission Error Confirm Manage Catalog permissions are active in Business settings Synchronization Lag Allow time for the initial data fetch on largescale catalogs Copyright 2026  WAPI  WhatsApp Marketing Platform by PixelStrap"
