    "url": "contacts.html",
    "title": "Contact Management",
    "content": "Contact Management  Wapi documentation Top Purchase Support Frontend Admin A A A Wapi documentation Contact Management Close Introduction Prerequisite Wapi Installation Overview Frontend Installation Backend Installation Local Server Live Server Database Seed Deployment Cpanel Virtual Private Server Vercel Core Features Advanced Features Usage Admin Usage Tenant Usage Agent Usage Admin Guide Dashboard Payment Transactions Users Short Links Subscription Manage Plans Subscriber Plans Manage Users All Users Add User Content Management Manage FAQs Manage Testimonials Pages Roles  Permissions Manage Landing Templates Library System Settings Payment Gateways Settings AI Models Languages Currencies Taxes Contact Inquiries Frontend Guide Dashboard WA Chat Chat Appearance Integrations Integrate WABA WABA Phone Numbers Templates Tools Tags Media Teams Agents Automations Automation Builder Predefined Actions Response Resources Keyword Trigger AI Call Assistant WhatsApp Form My Subscription Subscriptions Marketing Campaigns Orders Catalogues Webhooks Contacts Columns Import Jobs AI Config Developer Menu Contact Management 1 Overview The Contact Management module serves as the primary CRM hub for Wapi It enables businesses to centralize organize and segment their customer database for highly targeted WhatsApp campaigns and automated workflows Centralized Hub Consolidate leads from every touchpointcampaigns forms and chatbotsinto a single actionable database with realtime tracking 2 Operational Infrastructure The Contacts interface is designed for highvisibility management providing realtime data on your customer growth and limits Command  Control Health Metrics Realtime tracking of contact count vs plan limits eg 9992  10000 Global Discovery Instant keyword search to locate customers by name or phone number Dynamic Columns Customize the data grid to show specific attributes relevant to your sales flow Pro Tip Use the Refresh button periodically to resync the contact index and ensure realtime accuracy across team members 3 Data Attribute Taxonomy Wapi captures a rich spectrum of customer data points to enable highfidelity personalization and lead scoring Phone Identity Mandatory unique identifier with country code for WhatsApp delivery Lead Tags Dynamic labels Lead VIP Refund for segmentbased messaging Lead Source Track origin Ads Website QR to measure campaign ROI Firmographics Capture Company Name and Business association for B2B flows Preference Set preferred language to localize automated responses Sales Notes Internal context and private notes for agenttoagent visibility 4 Provisioning Protocol Step 1 Initiation  Click the  Add Contact button on the dashboard header Step 2 Mandatory Entry  Input the customers phone number including the country code no spaces Step 3 Intelligence Enrichment  Assign tags lead source and sales notes to categorize the lead Step 4 Database Sync  Click Create Contact to finalize and store the lead in the active CRM 5 Operational Synergy Scalable Data Management Contact Management achieves its full potential when paired with Bulk Operations Import thousands of leads via CSV to instantly trigger Welcome Campaigns or Automation Flows Workflow Example Import 1000 leads from a marketing campaign CSV Assign them the tag Winter_Sale_Lead Trigger a WhatsApp Broadcast specifically for that tag Update status to Active as responses come in Strategic Use Cases Lead Management Onboard cold leads for automated nurturing CRM Sync Sync data with external tools via bulk export Retention Segment by Loyalty tags for exclusive offers 6 Strategic Governance Integrity  Maintenance Consistent Tagging Use standardized tag formats to prevent segmentation clutter Data Cleanup Periodically audit and remove duplicate entries for cleaner reporting Masking Awareness Note that sensitive contact details are masked in the UI for security Troubleshooting If an import fails verify that your CSV structure matches the Wapi mapping and that no mandatory fields Phone Number are empty Copyright 2026  WAPI  WhatsApp Marketing Platform by PixelStrap"
