    "url": "cpanel.html",
    "title": "Introduction",
    "content": "Introduction  Wapi documentation Top Purchase Support Frontend Admin A A A Wapi documentation Chat collaborate and create teams effortlessly with Wapi Close Introduction Prerequisite Wapi Installation Overview Frontend Installation Backend Installation Local Server Live Server Database Seed Deployment Cpanel Virtual Private Server Vercel Core Features Advanced Features Usage Admin Usage Tenant Usage Agent Usage Admin Guide Dashboard Payment Transactions Users Short Links Subscription Manage Plans Subscriber Plans Manage Users All Users Add User Content Management Manage FAQs Manage Testimonials Pages Roles  Permissions Manage Landing Templates Library System Settings Payment Gateways Settings AI Models Languages Currencies Taxes Contact Inquiries Frontend Guide Dashboard WA Chat Chat Appearance Integrations Integrate WABA WABA Phone Numbers Templates Tools Tags Media Teams Agents Automations Automation Builder Predefined Actions Response Resources Keyword Trigger AI Call Assistant WhatsApp Form My Subscription Subscriptions Marketing Campaigns Orders Catalogues Webhooks Contacts Columns Import Jobs AI Config Developer Menu Deploying Wapi on cPanel We dont recommend deploying the Wapi backend on cPanel because it doesnt provide the flexibility or runtime control needed to manage background services and realtime functionalities effectively Prerequisites cPanel Hosting Ensure your hosting plan supports Nodejs and has sufficient resources FTP Access Obtain FTP credentials for file uploads Domain Configuration Verify that your domain is correctly pointed to your cPanel account Frontend Deployment React  Vite Step 1 Configure Vite for Production export default defineConfig base httpsyourdomaincom  Step 2 Build the Application npm install npm run build Step 3 Upload to cPanel Log in to cPanel and navigate to File Manager  Go to the public_html directory or subdirectory for subdomain Click Upload and select the distzip file Extract the uploaded zip file Step 4 Configure htaccess for SPA Routing ul liIfModule mod_rewritecli liRewriteEngine Onli liRewriteBase li liRewriteRule indexhtml  Lli liRewriteCond REQUEST_FILENAME fli liRewriteCond REQUEST_FILENAME dli liRewriteCond REQUEST_FILENAME lli liRewriteRule  indexhtml Lli liIfModuleli ul Whats Next Lets get started  your teams new home is Wapi Chat Prerequisite Required tools and setup Deploy on VPS VPS deployment setup guide Deploy on Vercel Vercel deployment guide steps Copyright 2026  WAPI  WhatsApp Marketing Platform by PixelStrap"
