    "url": "custom-sms.html",
    "title": "Introduction",
    "content": "Introduction  Wapi documentation Top Purchase Support Frontend Admin A A A Wapi documentation Chat collaborate and create teams effortlessly with Wapi Close Introduction Prerequisite Wapi Installation Overview Frontend Installation Backend Installation Local Server Live Server Database Seed Deployment Cpanel Virtual Private Server Vercel Core Features Advanced Features Usage Admin Usage Tenant Usage Agent Usage Admin Guide Dashboard Payment Transactions Users Short Links Subscription Manage Plans Subscriber Plans Manage Users All Users Add User Content Management Manage FAQs Manage Testimonials Pages Roles  Permissions Manage Landing Templates Library System Settings Payment Gateways Settings AI Models Languages Currencies Taxes Contact Inquiries Frontend Guide Dashboard WA Chat Chat Appearance Integrations Integrate WABA WABA Phone Numbers Templates Tools Tags Media Teams Agents Automations Automation Builder Predefined Actions Response Resources Keyword Trigger AI Call Assistant WhatsApp Form My Subscription Subscriptions Marketing Campaigns Orders Catalogues Webhooks Contacts Columns Import Jobs AI Config Developer Menu Wapi Super Admin 10 Custom SMS Gateway The Custom SMS Gateway page allows the admin to configure any thirdparty SMS provider by entering the required API details and authentication credentials These settings determine how SMS messagesespecially login OTPsare sent from the system Admins Can Configure  Base URL The API endpoint of the SMS provider eg Twilio MSG91 custom API  HTTP Method Choose the request type POSTGET required by the SMS provider  Configs SID Auth Token Custom Keys Set the providerspecific credentials like SID Auth Token or any custom fields needed for authentication  ID  Auth Token  From Number Credentials used for messaging authorization and the senders phone number  Custom Keys Dynamic Parameters Add additional API parameters in keyvalue format as required by the provider  Request Body JSON or Formdata Customize the structure of the message body that will be sent to the SMS API Once configured these credentials are used whenever a user logs in using the OTP login method The OTP SMS is automatically sent through the gateway configured on this page ensuring seamless authentication Whats Next Lets get started  your teams new home is Wapi Chat Super Admin Dashboard Access global insights and analytics SMS Gateways Choose the preferred SMS provider directly from the admin panel WebRTC Highquality audiovideo calling Copyright 2026  WAPI  WhatsApp Marketing Platform by PixelStrap"
