    "content": "Payment Gateway  Wapi documentation Top Purchase Support Frontend Admin A A A Wapi documentation Payment Gateway Overview Close Introduction Prerequisite Wapi Installation Overview Frontend Installation Backend Installation Local Server Live Server Database Seed Deployment Cpanel Virtual Private Server Vercel Core Features Advanced Features Usage Admin Usage Tenant Usage Agent Usage Admin Guide Dashboard Payment Transactions Users Short Links Subscription Manage Plans Subscriber Plans Manage Users All Users Add User Content Management Manage FAQs Manage Testimonials Pages Roles  Permissions Manage Landing Templates Library System Settings Payment Gateways Settings AI Models Languages Currencies Taxes Contact Inquiries Frontend Guide Dashboard WA Chat Chat Appearance Integrations Integrate WABA WABA Phone Numbers Templates Tools Tags Media Teams Agents Automations Automation Builder Predefined Actions Response Resources Keyword Trigger AI Call Assistant WhatsApp Form My Subscription Subscriptions Marketing Campaigns Orders Catalogues Webhooks Contacts Columns Import Jobs AI Config Developer Menu Payment Gateway Overview The Payment Gateway module allows administrators to configure and manage payment processing systems for the WAPI WhatsApp marketing platform This module supports multiple payment providers including Stripe and Razorpay to accommodate different regional requirements Configuration Options Stripe Integration Configure Stripe API keys and settings for credit card processing Razorpay Integration Set up Razorpay credentials for alternative payment processing API Keys Management Securely store and manage payment gateway credentials Webhook Configuration Set up payment confirmation and event handling Copyright 2026  WAPI  WhatsApp Marketing Platform by PixelStrap"
