    "content": "User Subscriptions  Wapi documentation Top Purchase Support Frontend Admin A A A Wapi documentation User Subscriptions Overview Close Introduction Prerequisite Wapi Installation Overview Frontend Installation Backend Installation Local Server Live Server Database Seed Deployment Cpanel Virtual Private Server Vercel Core Features Advanced Features Usage Admin Usage Tenant Usage Agent Usage Admin Guide Dashboard Payment Transactions Users Short Links Subscription Manage Plans Subscriber Plans Manage Users All Users Add User Content Management Manage FAQs Manage Testimonials Pages Roles  Permissions Manage Landing Templates Library System Settings Payment Gateways Settings AI Models Languages Currencies Taxes Contact Inquiries Frontend Guide Dashboard WA Chat Chat Appearance Integrations Integrate WABA WABA Phone Numbers Templates Tools Tags Media Teams Agents Automations Automation Builder Predefined Actions Response Resources Keyword Trigger AI Call Assistant WhatsApp Form My Subscription Subscriptions Marketing Campaigns Orders Catalogues Webhooks Contacts Columns Import Jobs AI Config Developer Menu User Subscriptions Overview The User Subscriptions module allows administrators to monitor manage and analyze all active and past subscriptions on the WAPI WhatsApp marketing platform This module provides insights into user subscription patterns and helps manage billing relationships Subscription Monitoring Active Subscriptions View all currently active subscriptions with details on plan billing date and payment status Subscription History Track all past subscriptions and cancellations Payment Status Monitor payment successfailure for each subscription Renewal Dates Track upcoming renewal dates for proactive management User Details See which users are subscribed to which plans Management Capabilities Subscription Modifications Update user subscription plans when needed Manual Renewals Process renewals for users experiencing payment issues Refund Processing Handle refund requests and cancellations Plan UpgradesDowngrades Manage transitions between different plan tiers Analytics Analyze subscription trends and user retention Copyright 2026  WAPI  WhatsApp Marketing Platform by PixelStrap"
